metadata.creator: Spencer Putt
metadata.description:
The 1.06.6 Android APK of WabbitEmu, an emulator for Z80-based TI graphing calculators like the TI-83+.

The app was available on the Play Store, but became unavailable late in 2021 for unclear reasons; this version is the most recent one from the Play Store as of that time.
